title: King Dy-zoff Pads 80-ct.
description:
Product Description
Simple, sanitary, convenient pads contain DY-Zoff, used to remove color and tint stains from skin (forehead, nape of the neck) after colors have set. 80-ct.

The most convenient way to remove hair color stains from skin.
The only stain remover that eliminates the need for cotton and towels.
Single-use cotton pads- just dispose after each use. A necessary addition to every Colorist's station.
Saturated with the unique Dy-Zoff formula to instantly wipe away stains.
Pads are always moist and fresh- ready at any time.
